data.description: Come see this breathtaking french style custom home on 2 acres of land. This GEM is packed with upgrades & amenities including 2 master suites w/walk-through showers, hearth room, formal dining, scored concrete floors, gleaming hardwood floors, fabulous gourmet kitchen, gas cooking, media room, bonus room w/a wet bar, office area, sizable bedrooms, 4 fireplaces, front & rear stairs, & much MORE! Meticulously maintained! Enjoy the tranquil lush backyard & a superb covered patio for entertaining!!
